            "reviews": "“Tiny Troopers is a cute little war game that takes me back to my Hogs of War playing days.”<br>70 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://darkzero.co.uk/game-reviews/tiny-troopers-pc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Dark Zero</a><br><br>“If you do like top-down shooters and cartoony games in general, give it a try.”<br>72 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.gamrreview.com/review/89239/tiny-troopers-pc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >gamrreview</a><br><br>“Tiny Troopers delivers a delicious bite sized portion of Cannon Fodder-style shenanigans featuring a compelling economy system and heartbreaking permanent deaths.”<br>80 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.dealspwn.com/tiny-troopers-review-cannon-fodder-3-113621\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Dealspwn</a><br>",
